Geislingen: More than 100 young catholics of small Heuberg affirm their confession with the confirmation
In two services is 101 15 - and 16-year old young people of the pastoral care unit at small Heuberg gefirmt.
The group of Laudato SI accompanied the service, in the afternoon the youth choir The Spirit in the morning.
With the receipt of the Firmsakraments the young people said yes to their baptism and requested the strength of the holy spirit.
The Firmlinge had themselves in the past months, under which line of deacon and the assistance of numerous community members prepares Reiner Dehner for the large holiday.
In different projects they became acquainted with thereby different tasks of the Christian community life and experienced together the youth day in Untermachtal.
